channel.title: Barnacles spitting gibs stuck in ceiling + houndeye thing
channel.description: Very often when barnacle drops human gibs after being killed, a majority of them suffocates into ceiling and becomes stuck. I also noticed than barnacles can't catch and eat living houndeyes. They should, considering they are lighter than human body, which they can pull (proof: you can pick up houndeye body while you cannot human's)
